{"tid":2234181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天下黑警一樣黑，澳門黑警呃賭廳現金碼","createTime":"2020-10-07T16:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T07:37:22.000Z","uid":169310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f265d40dcbde927e842e1150184a81738a0ce0bc","tid":2234181,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"【#知法犯法】疑因疫情關係，本澳部分貴賓廳無法提現。爛賭紀律部隊成員以此為契機，與妻以&ldquo;有路數&rdquo;兌現為由，上月初詐騙兩名本地男子共一千萬港元現金籌碼，旋即到賭場狂賭7日，終於輸個精光，隨後被對方不斷追數，簽下欠單且償還一百多萬元後&ldquo;潛水&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n兩事主報警，司警在本月五日及六日，在關閘口岸截獲涉案妻子，並在台山區單位帶查涉案丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n該名紀律部隊成員姓陳，三十多歲，2006年入職；妻子二十五歲，持雙程證。司警今日將兩人移送檢察院偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n#貴賓廳 #提現 #一千萬港元現金籌碼 #紀律部隊成員 #澳門日報 #澳日<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n更多即時新聞，請下載澳門日報應用程式！<br />\n立即下載： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZcTetq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZcTetq&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Au0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=f461e867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZcTetq</a><br />\n即時關注埋澳門日報其他平台，掌握更多資訊！<br />\nTelegram：<a href=\"https://t.me/macaodaily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmacaodaily&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Au0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=548008ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/macaodaily</a><br />\nYouTube：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KLn447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KLn447&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Au0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=2849a2b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KLn447</a><br />\nWeibo：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZbKlFu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZbKlFu&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Au0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=42b8bcbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZbKlFu</a><br />\nInstagram：macaodaily<br />\nWeChat：澳門日報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://appimg.modaily.cn/app/displayTemplate1/dist/index.html#/newsDetail/9758086/0?isShare=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.co